    "However, it necessitated a relatively extended training duration, with an average training time of 8.45 minutes.",
    "The (CNN-LSTM) model, despite its complexity with 16,799,497 parameters, demonstrated competitive performance and required slightly fewer iterations compared to other algorithms, as shown in Fig. 8.Conversely, both the Bi-LSTM and (LSTM) models delivered acceptable results, with accuracy rates of 96.65% and 98.75%, respectively.",
